    example: "In Llama 3.1 8B, Relation.Conjunction neurons activate on list-like structures regardless of explicit conjunctions — 'apples, oranges, bananas' produces Conjunction neuron firing despite the absence of 'and', because the comma-separated list structure is itself a conjunction signal. This is how models recognize implicit enumeration without always requiring explicit connectives.",
